short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extention shows vitthala's devotional abhang

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pandurang Vitthal is an chrome extention to display devotional abhang of Pandurang Vitthal, Sant Dnyaneshwar, Sant Tukaram, Sant Namdev, Sant Eknath and many more vitthal sant .

There is an associate android application which helps you to get Pandurang Vitthal information, Gatha, Abhang, Dnyaneshwari, Haripath, Pasaydan and many more devotional literature and nearby hindu temples.
